messages.message: Looking for someone to help lead/take ownership of the IB Onboarding Session “How to Use Instabase”,  which occurs approximately every two weeks and is an hour long, and goes through an existing slide deck describing out mindset, and then through the creation of a Refiner program. Any volunteers for this would be really appreciated! If we find multiple people, we can also make it so it happens with low frequency for each person
Also it is typically held Tuesday mornings
I’ve done the self learn training videos, so could probably do this :slightly_smiling_face:

Hi Aaron, I’ve delivered two basics training to JPMC so far (flow and Refiner), so if you think it’s enough to deliver the onboarding one hour session, then I’ll also volunteer as I have capacity at the moment .
Lets let Seb do it, Seb’s better :wink:
@Ben , we can share the duty with others if more volunteer, I’m not sure I’m better though :slightly_smiling_face:
you guys so cute and polite. You would both be awesome at this! share the responsibility
Really appreciate it :slightly_smiling_face: I will message you both regarding details
